```

---

## ğŸ”„ Special Directory Symbols

| Symbol | Meaning           |
| ------ | ----------------- |
| `.`    | Current directory |
| `..`   | Parent directory  |
| `~`    | Home directory    |
| `/`    | Root directory    |

---

## ğŸ“‚ Creating Directories

### `mkdir` â€“ Make Directory

